{"tid":1382931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「連儂牆」是社會破裂的禍根","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:10:05.000Z","uid":173849,"like":265,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"b72fc27fa2f27959ac5bcc9a2466e87cd051c676","tid":1382931,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/07/29/010122505.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ftopic%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F010122505.shtml&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=8ee614af\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2019/07/29/010122505.shtml</a><br />\n文：朱家健<br />\n曾幾何時，這座城市有歡笑，有喜悅，卻在惡魔和喪屍傀儡的恐嚇下，「連儂牆」在各區、大學、甚至創新科技署的辦公室內築起，這些連儂牆象徵仇恨和敵意，倒像《魔神英雄傳》內被魔鬼征服的星界山，市民被恐嚇，生活在無奈的壓力中。<br />\n<br />\n一張又一張字跡類同的彩色便條，「不約而同」地在各社區出現，像烹飪節目的菜餚「因時間關係，已預先準備好」，為的是供人家拍照而已。有些「連儂牆」甚至波及附近的學校、巴士站牌和扶手欄杆，並佔據了整個行人隧道，更恐怖的是把行人隧道佈置成靈堂，嚇窒路人。<br />\n<br />\n細看「連儂牆」上便條的內容，不堪入目，有的抹黑特區政府和警隊，有的具誹謗及誤導成分，有的煽動他人犯罪，有的具煽惑仇恨和暴力，有的歧視宗教和種族，有的粗言穢語，也有情色性騷擾的字句，都不是好東西！<br />\n<br />\n「連儂牆」傳播負能量，也有損市容。<span style=\"color: red;\">胡亂把便條貼在隧道和牆上，是破壞公物，部分便條更覆蓋了隧道的燈泡，遮掩了照明和視線，會引起過熱甚至起火，並構成治安問題；女士晚上歸家也提心吊膽，單車使用者的視線也會因「連儂牆」而受阻，增加發生意外風險。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一個「連儂牆」「重災區」，是政府官地和公物，郵筒、郵包存放箱、電箱、巴士站、欄杆、燈柱等無一幸免，破壞者已觸犯刑事毀壞罪，不能再賊喊捉賊，而且也是在非法佔用官地，特區政府部門更應該牽頭清理這些不雅和不當的便條。部分破壞者也在未徵求物主或業權持有人同意，擅自把「連儂牆」張貼在私人地方，同樣涉民事侵權行為。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">部分「連儂牆」針對的對象，屬區議員或政客，部分人或有意競逐年底的區議會選舉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「連儂牆」的作者或涉違反《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》(香港法例第554章)有關作出某些關乎候選人或準候選人的欺騙性行為的舞弊行為、對候選人或準候選人施用武力或脅迫手段、或威脅對候選人或準候選人施用武力或脅迫手段的舞弊行為。廉政公署可作出適當跟進。<br />\n<br />\n「連儂牆」如張貼他人的相片，或已涉刑事恐嚇罪，並涉侵犯版權持有人的知識產權，而披露他人的資料，也是違反相關保障私隱的法例，個人資料私隱專員公署可作出適當跟進。<br />\n<br />\n是包容？是霸道？旁觀者已一目了然，「連儂牆」撕裂社會，敲碎了人與人之間的和睦與互信，是社會的悲劇。「連儂牆」也成為這場禍港奪權「顏色革命」的「道具」，為不明勢力的敵人助攻，親者痛，仇者快！香港是法治社會，也有高效政府，食環署、地政總署等部分應主動執法，移除妖物，還原官地和公物，還我們一個乾淨和平靜的社區。<br />\n<br />\n作者為全國港澳研究會香港特邀會員、香港基本法澳門基本法研究會會員、中國和平統一促進會香港總會常務理事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保皇狗驚到瀨屎<br />\n證明連儂牆好撚有用</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde6c94df2faa11b8535ddb2a5f79d8b88f53020","tid":1382931,"uid":44358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"撕一貼百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fcc53c2e56b45c5a198e9c003724ccf8934ec2","tid":1382931,"uid":54721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"魔神英雄傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e6a6f928e7735e3f98313772349af38d9582ed","tid":1382931,"uid":12558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"連memo紙都驚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6324582b7ca025d7ffbb876e1761ed161eeb3b5c","tid":1382931,"uid":36378,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"慢慢同佢地玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b08b69d1e1d97035223bc23c84d1ee26dbc687","tid":1382931,"uid":108854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"做好文宣 邊區連儂牆經常被撕 約埋一齊去貼百<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382944</a><br />\n<br />\n特別係港島區 <br />\n召喚港島人！"},{"pid":"85fb88ba58f5f37c3e47fd4755718af50488c3aa","tid":1382931,"uid":80725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"連儂牆就好似一個社區連登咁<br />\n將連登放左上每區, 又做到報告板宣佈活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cbc3be6649cfb3b0885ca89c56d85c893325c2","tid":1382931,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e6a6f928e7735e3f98313772349af38d9582ed","tid":1382931,"uid":12558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"連memo紙都驚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04153be9ba5907ffeffef6d8c1745edddfbb4975","tid":1382931,"uid":149008,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"亂撚噏無閪腦，祝你早日升天唔好